I chose to confess, and handed
over the money voluntarily.

734
01:10:42,930 --> 01:10:45,370
Full confession, Comrade Captain.
Let's just call it that.

735
01:10:46,490 --> 01:10:48,210
Drink, bitch.

736
01:10:50,690 --> 01:10:52,210
I'll finish it.

737
01:11:10,370 --> 01:11:13,050
Nineteen thousand,
minus liquor and cigarettes.

738
01:11:13,090 --> 01:11:16,210
Where's the rest?
Are you holding out?

739
01:11:16,370 --> 01:11:19,090
I can put some money in
if necessary.

740
01:11:20,370 --> 01:11:23,600
Write up the nineteen thousand
at the accounting office.

741
01:11:23,730 --> 01:11:26,200
How much did they take?
- You can take the money.

742
01:11:26,250 --> 01:11:29,640
We already wrote it off. That's not
the issue: First, AWOL, theft,

743
01:11:29,690 --> 01:11:32,330
a dead police officer; suicide...

744
01:11:32,690 --> 01:11:37,450
What did you do to make that soldier jump?
- How much money do I have to add?

745
01:11:37,610 --> 01:11:42,290
Write up Private Tugayev, Comrade Captain.
Officially, at the garrison.

746
01:11:42,570 --> 01:11:45,850
We'll start an investigation,
file a case. He's going to jail.

747
01:11:46,130 --> 01:11:48,690
Everyone is sick of disorderly conduct.

748
01:11:58,050 --> 01:11:59,730
What do you want?

749
01:12:00,770 --> 01:12:02,760
I request that you let the AWOL go.

750
01:12:03,250 --> 01:12:06,640
The kid won't survive military jail.
- Why not?

751
01:12:07,890 --> 01:12:09,690
Shrieks like a bird.

752
01:12:11,370 --> 01:12:12,970
Too late.

753
01:12:16,090 --> 01:12:19,640
Wanna hear a joke
about a cat and mouse?

754
01:12:19,730 --> 01:12:21,170
OK.

755
01:12:21,770 --> 01:12:25,890
A cat goes hunting in the basement.
Walks in, sees a pair of huge eyes.

756
01:12:25,930 --> 01:12:29,210
He gets scared and goes, "Who are you?"
"A mouse".

757
01:12:29,330 --> 01:12:32,450
"Why do you have such huge eyes?"
- "I'm shitting".

758
01:12:32,530 --> 01:12:34,250
What do you want?

759
01:12:35,930 --> 01:12:40,210
Not funny, huh?
- Nah, it's OK.

760
01:12:46,850 --> 01:12:51,130
Let the AWOL go, bro.
He'll die in jail.

761
01:12:52,170 --> 01:12:55,090
I can't.
- Why not?

762
01:12:55,370 --> 01:12:58,760
Too late, bro. Can't do it.

763
01:12:59,090 --> 01:13:00,650
Why not?

764
01:13:01,170 --> 01:13:04,850
Everyone is sick of disorderly conduct.

765
01:13:19,810 --> 01:13:22,770
It's time, Comrade Captain.
We're on a schedule.

766
01:13:23,050 --> 01:13:24,610
Five minutes.

767
01:13:36,810 --> 01:13:38,410
Where does it hurt?

768
01:13:40,370 --> 01:13:43,680
It hurts here.
- No, it doesn't hurt there.

769
01:13:48,370 --> 01:13:51,050
Don't let them take me right away,
Comrade Captain.

770
01:13:52,650 --> 01:13:55,120
Let me stay here a while.

771
01:14:04,210 --> 01:14:06,200
You know where it hurts, kid?

772
01:14:06,530 --> 01:14:09,530
Where?
- Nowhere.

773
01:14:13,570 --> 01:14:15,370
Soon, Comrade Captain?

774
01:14:16,970 --> 01:14:19,280
Don't let them take me right away,
Comrade Captain.

775
01:14:19,930 --> 01:14:22,690
I don't need this.
What's so special about him?

776
01:14:23,890 --> 01:14:26,570
What have I done, Comrade Captain?

777
01:14:30,050 --> 01:14:32,730
What have I done, Comrade Captain?

778
01:14:33,450 --> 01:14:36,490
Stand up! Atten-hut!

779
01:14:37,690 --> 01:14:39,490
Forward march!

780
01:15:27,690 --> 01:15:29,290
I feel bad for the kid.

781
01:15:29,930 --> 01:15:33,010
Though he was a complete idiot.
I could tell right away.

782
01:15:35,330 --> 01:15:37,610
What now, Comrade Captain?
Back to the unit, eh?

783
01:15:38,570 --> 01:15:41,170
Give the government's money back,
sign for it, right?

784
01:15:42,210 --> 01:15:45,210
What time is lunch, Comrade Captain?
Is it time yet?

785
01:15:46,930 --> 01:15:50,080
Please forgive me, Comrade Captain.
Please don't.

786
01:15:50,450 --> 01:15:53,370
You want to punish me? Go ahead,
just don't put me in jail.

787
01:15:54,610 --> 01:15:58,970
Comrade Captain, please forgive me.

788
01:16:00,210 --> 01:16:03,250
Comrade Captain, please don't.

789
01:16:04,410 --> 01:16:06,690
Please forgive me, Comrade Captain.

790
01:16:09,290 --> 01:16:11,170
Comrade Captain...

791
01:16:26,930 --> 01:16:28,410
Thank you.

792
01:16:31,210 --> 01:16:33,330
Thank you, Comrade Captain.

793
01:16:35,370 --> 01:16:37,360
Just don't put me in jail.

794
01:16:43,490 --> 01:16:45,610
Promise me, Comrade Captain.

795
01:16:49,490 --> 01:16:51,960
I have your word, yeah?

